<p>How can I transform all <code>"</code>  present in a string to <code>&amp;quot;</code> ?</p>  <p>Example:</p>  <p><strong>Source Data:</strong> <code>&lt;String&gt;"ACCOUNT_DETAILS" : "75"&lt;/String&gt;</code></p>  <p><strong>Target Data:</strong> <code>&lt;String&gt;&amp;quot;ACCOUNT_DETAILS&amp;quot; : &amp;quot;75&amp;quot;&lt;/String&gt;</code></p>  <p>PS: I am using XSLT 1.0. I tried discussion at "<a href="http://stackoverflow.com/questions/3067113/xslt-string-replace">XSLT string replace</a>" but it's not working.</p>